propDescriptions.component: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.slotProps: The props used for each slot inside the TabsList.
propDescriptions.slots: The components used for each slot inside the TabsList. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component. See Slots API below for more details.

slotDescriptions.root: The component used to render the root.
